# ollij.fi realtime games — WebSocket endpoint on the box.
#
# The static site (ollij.fi, including /aumann) is served by GitHub Pages via
# Cloudflare; this box runs only the Node games server. The browser connects to
# wss://ws.ollij.fi, which Caddy reverse-proxies to the games server (the Node
# process serves /socket.io/* and /health). Caddy obtains and renews the HTTPS
# certificate automatically via the ACME HTTP-01 challenge — so ws.ollij.fi must
# resolve to this box and reach it on port 80. Keep the ws.ollij.fi record
# DNS-only (grey cloud) in Cloudflare so the challenge isn't intercepted.

ws.ollij.fi {
	encode zstd gzip
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8787
}
